  "translations": {
    "en": "and said: Why did the people abandon Ali (peace be upon him), when his closeness to the Messenger of God (may God bless him and his family) was such, and his position among the Muslims was such, and his striving for Islam was such?",
    "ur": "اور کہا: لوگوں نے علی علیہ السلام کو کیوں چھوڑ دیا؟",
    "tr": "ve dedim: İnsanlar neden Ali'yi (a.s.) terk etti?",
    "fa": "و گفتم: چرا مردم علی علیه السلام را ترک کردند؟",
    "id": "dan berkata: Mengapa orang-orang meninggalkan Ali (a.s.)?",
    "bn": "এবং বললাম: মানুষেরা কেন আলী (আ.)-কে পরিত্যাগ করল?",
    "es": "y dije: ¿Por qué la gente abandonó a Ali (la paz sea con él)?",
    "fr": "et j'ai dit : Pourquoi les gens ont-ils abandonné Ali (que la paix soit sur lui) ?",
    "de": "und sagte: Warum haben die Menschen Ali (Friede sei mit ihm) verlassen?",
    "ru": "и сказал: Почему люди покинули Али (мир ему)?",
    "zh": "说道：人们为何抛弃了阿里（愿主赐他平安）？"
  }
